00:08:56,017 --> 00:08:57,102
Dia tinggi dan kurus.

124
00:08:58,436 --> 00:08:59,437
Korban kecelakaan.

125
00:09:04,818 --> 00:09:05,902
Maksudku, donornya.

126
00:09:06,695 --> 00:09:08,113
Donor lever untuk Ji-a.

127
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,449
Aku tak bisa memberi tahu

128
00:09:12,242 --> 00:09:14,786
