beserta gambarnya.

144
00:10:26,274 --> 00:10:28,234
Baik. Terima kasih. Akan kulakukan.

145
00:10:28,985 --> 00:10:32,197
- Aku tetap cemas.
- Tak perlu cemas.

146
00:10:32,405 --> 00:10:34,991
Kontraksinya terkendali,
dan kondisi bayi baik.

147
00:10:35,575 --> 00:10:38,620
- Dia akan baik-baik saja.
- Apa harus terus pakai obat?

148
00:10:38,703 --> 00:10:42,040
Seperti sudah dijelaskan, obatnya aman.

149
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:45,335
Biar kujelaskan sekali lagi.

150
00:10:45,418 --> 00:10:46,503
Sebentar.

151
00:10:46,586 --> 00:10:49,172
Pasien itu, Park Mi-jeong.
