00:10:49,255 --> 00:10:50,548
- Tunggu.
- Sepanjang 1,5 cm.

153
00:10:51,424 --> 00:10:52,258
Rupanya 1,5 cm.

154
00:10:53,093 --> 00:10:55,261
- Dokter Chu Min-ha.
- Ya, Dokter.

