00:10:55,386 --> 00:10:58,264
Pasien bedah cesar banyak berdarah
karena kontraksinya buruk.

156
00:10:58,348 --> 00:11:00,558
Cek pembalut dan awasi kontraksinya.

157
00:11:00,642 --> 00:11:01,684
Baik, Dokter.

158
00:11:03,228 --> 00:11:07,482
