165
00:11:21,871 --> 00:11:23,331
tetapi mengalami takikardia.

166
00:11:23,414 --> 00:11:26,376
Kurangi jadi delapan gtt,
dan cek tanda vitalnya satu jam lagi.

167
00:11:26,459 --> 00:11:27,293
Baik.

168
00:11:28,336 --> 00:11:29,587
Gunanya untuk membuat bayi

169
00:11:29,671 --> 00:11:32,507
