Tidak ada hematoma.

179
00:12:01,411 --> 00:12:03,496
Dokter, tolong cek NST ini.

180
00:12:03,580 --> 00:12:05,331
Janin Jeong Min-gyeong
menunjukkan pelambatan.

181
00:12:06,124 --> 00:12:08,084
