00:13:10,939 --> 00:13:12,106
RUANG PERAWAT

204
00:13:12,190 --> 00:13:13,024
Permisi.

205
00:13:14,609 --> 00:13:15,485
Ya.

206
00:13:18,237 --> 00:13:21,824
Aku akan cek pembalut pasien bedah cesar.

207
00:13:21,908 --> 00:13:22,867
Baik.

208
00:13:26,621 --> 00:13:30,208
Astaga. Pertempuran beruang dan rubah.

209
