320
00:19:15,553 --> 00:19:17,221
Ya, pacarnya sekampus.

321
00:19:17,305 --> 00:19:19,515
- Dokter Lee Ik-jun?
- Ik-jun?

322
00:19:19,599 --> 00:19:22,310
Tidak. Mereka tidak pernah berpacaran.

323
