613
00:38:51,364 --> 00:38:53,408
Operasi dalam kondisi sadar memang sulit.

614
00:38:54,492 --> 00:38:57,620
Seperti dijelaskan sebelumnya,
dalam kasus Kim Hyeon-su,

615
00:38:57,704 --> 00:39:01,040
